The Caretaker Committee Chairman of Iganna Local Council Development Area in Oyo State, Comrade Jacob Olayiwola Adeleke, has been kidnapped. DAILY POST gathered that the council boss was kidnapped Sunday evening. He was kidnapped alongside his driver. Sources who confirmed the incident, said that Adeleke and his driver were kidnapped along Okeho-Ado Awaye Road. All effort by DAILY POST to get reaction from the Police Spokesman, Olugbenga Fadeyi proved abortive as calls put through to his mobile phone were not answered. Details laterâ€¦